  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "KEYBOARD MACROS",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "KEYBOARD MACROS"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Keyboard macros are strings of keyboard events.  To create one,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "a macro is recorded by watching the keyboard input in one SPF"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "session.  At a later time, the previously recorded macro may"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "be played back, and each of the events that were typed during"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the original recording are re-executed in the new context."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For example, if you are a COBOL programmer that frequently types"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PERFORM structures, a PERFORM template could be assigned to a"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "key macro for later playback.  The template would contain"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "just the keywords that are required, and you could fill in the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "variable expressions and code."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "A simple PERFORM block may look as follows:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PERFORM UNTIL"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "code"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "END-PERFORM"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
